      "text": "Alright, one small iced vanilla latte."
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anything else for you today?"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That’s all."
    },
    {
